template(name='main')
  +header
  .col-md-12.headerDescriptionContainer
    p.col-md-6.col-md-offset-3.headerDescription
      | NIAM displays the diseases mentioned in ProMED-mail posts.
      | A disease's novelty can be assessed through its time since the previous
      | mention and through its ranking on the trending diseases list.
    p.col-md-8.col-md-offset-2 Click on a disease to see its historical mentions.
  .col-md-12.col-sm-12.col-xs-12
    ul.nav.nav-tabs
      li.col-md-2.col-sm-8.col-xs-12.active#recentPanelTab
        a(href='#recentPanel', data-toggle='tab') Recently Mentioned
      li.col-md-2.col-sm-8.col-xs-12#frequentPanelTab
        a(href='#frequentPanel', data-toggle='tab') Frequently Mentioned
      li.col-md-2.col-sm-8.col-xs-12#trendingPanelTab
        a(href='#trendingPanel', data-toggle='tab') Trending
    .tab-content
      #recentPanel.tab-pane.active
        #recentlyMentionedInfectiousAgents
      #frequentPanel.tab-pane
        #frequentlyMentionedInfectiousAgents
      #trendingPanel.tab-pane
        #trendingInfectiousAgents
  .clear
